{
  "chapter": 40,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙重伤昏迷九天后在观天楼醒来，赵倩与邹衍照料其间。邹衍自称因天象新星移至大梁上空，认定项少龙为新圣人，又因预知劫难而令纪嫣然及时相救。项少龙伤势渐愈，与赵倩打情骂俏，纪嫣然来探时二人互诉情意。纪嫣然告知信陵君、龙阳君、嚣魏牟正全力搜城，形势危急。三人谈及项少龙自行设计的索钩工具，纪嫣然叹其深不可测。突然警铃响，信陵君率人搜查观天楼，三人藏入邹衍设计的暗格，肢体交缠中项少龙偷吻纪嫣然。信陵君手下假冒邹衍声音引诱三人现身，项少龙识破诡计，邹衍返回后对项少龙机智大为赞叹。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "这是什么地方，我昏迷多久了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是老夫观天楼最高的第五层，少龙你昏迷了足有九天，换过别个人伤得这么重，失血这么多，早一命呜呼。但你非凡人，所以绝对死不了，可见天数有定，应验不爽！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "先生为何救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "邹先生真的对你有救命之恩，若非他精通医术，悉心医治你……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真正救你的人是纪嫣然，老夫只是适逢其会吧！这个观天楼乃老夫研究天文的地方，亦是大梁最高的建筑物，保没有人会查到这里来。况且老夫和你非亲非故，不会有人怀疑到老夫身上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "先生仍未回答我先前的问题。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事要由头说起。三年前，老夫在齐国发现一颗新星，移往天场上赵、魏交界的地方，便知这时代的新圣人终于出现，于是不远千里的来到大梁，找寻新主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "什么是天场？那里竟有赵国和魏国吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "天人交感，地上发生的每一件事，都是上应天兆。老夫五德终始之学，便是根据天上金、木、水、火、土五星而来，以天命论人事。天场就是把天上依照地上的国家地域分区，例如有客星犯天上某区的主星，那区的君主便有难，百应不爽。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "那和我有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "怎会和你没有关系？就在你来到大梁的同时，那颗新星刚好飞临天场上大梁的位置，于是邹某便知新圣人驾临。初见你时虽觉你有龙虎之姿，一时还未醒觉，到那晚你说出石破天惊的治国之论，终猜到你是新圣人，不过仍要到你那晚遇袭，始绝对肯定老夫没有看错你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "前一部分我可以明白，但为何我遇袭受伤，反更坚定先生的信念？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "在你遇袭那天的下午，纪小姐郁郁不乐回到雅湖小筑，被我再三追问，说你不肯追求她。于是老夫对她说，天上新星被另一颗星凌逼，恐怕你当晚会有劫难。因此纪小姐才能及时把你救出，送到老夫这里。试问少龙你若非新圣人，怎会如此巧合？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "倩儿！你消瘦了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "比起你为我的牺牲，这算什么，那晚看着你为怕我受伤，用身体硬挡贼子的利剑，人家的心都碎了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然姊三天没有来过，真使人挂心。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "她常来看我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她不知多么着紧你，每次来都帮我为你洗伤口和换药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "那岂非我身上什么地方都给你两人看遍？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "我定要报复，好好看遍我们公主的身体。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看便看吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "不但要看，还要用手来研究，公主反对吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不用怕！是嫣然来哩！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "小姐救命之恩，项少龙永世不忘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要说客气话，你复原的速度真是惊人，你不知那晚满身鲜血的样子多么吓人，累得人家都为你哭哩！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然还是第一次为男人哭哩！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然姊对你不知多么好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "看来我不但及格，还更进一步进入小姐的芳心里，对吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "对不起！仍只是在及格的阶段。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "只要及格便有机会，纪小姐不是会尽量方便我吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家千辛万苦来到这里，还坐到你身边来，不是正方便你吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "外面的情况如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "信陵君、龙阳君和嚣魏牟正全力搜寻你，城防比以前加强数倍，连城外和河道都布满关防和巡兵，恐怕变成鸟儿才可飞出去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "其他人呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！倩儿早问过嫣然姊，他们全部安全逃走，一个也没给逮着。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这几天魏人分区逐家逐户搜索你的行踪，最后终会搜到这里来。暂时他们只留意我，还没有怀疑到邹先生，可是一天你不离开大梁，仍是非常危险。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "姊姊你这么有本事，必定有办法的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我无时无刻不在想办法，但城防那么严。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你腰上佩带的那东西很奇怪，连邹先生那么见多识广的人都没见过，是从哪里弄来的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "那是我自己设计，由赵国的工匠打制的，只要到达城墙，我便有方法带倩儿越墙而去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "愈和你接触，愈发觉得你这人不可测度。不过现在的情况下，你想到达城墙不被哨楼上的人发现，根本没有可能，就算走出城外，亦避不过城外以万计的守军，所以还是要另想办法。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "姊姊是不是愈来愈喜欢他呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有敌人来了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "躲到哪里去？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是邹先生为自己设计的救命之所，想不到给我们用上了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "喂！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "本人还是第一次来参观邹先生的望天楼，噢！这是什么玩意？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "这是量度天星方位的仪器，邹某正准备绘制一幅精确的星图。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "噢！我还以为房内另有乾坤，原来是先生的卧室。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "我的工作只能在晚上进行，没有睡觉的地方怎行。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "不若让我到先生的观星台开开眼界。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可以出来哩！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "信陵君手下",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "君上真是多此一举，明明没有人，仍要我逐层楼扮邹衍叫唤三次，嘿！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "看来我并非什么新圣人，因为我完全没有圣人的定力。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
